%% Flow: execution session lifecycle — from timer fire to shutdown
%% Last updated: 2026-07-21
sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Timer/Trigger
    participant W as wake.sh
    participant GCal as Google Calendar API
    participant G as Gate Chain
    participant P as Pre-launch
    participant C as claude -p
    participant M as Memory

    T->>W: fire (nightly/emergency/manual)
    W->>G: Gate 0: check_usage.sh
    alt usage exceeded
        G-->>W: abort
    end

    alt TRIGGER_MODE=nightly
        W->>GCal: gcal_sync.py — fetch events (skip if <15 min since last sync)
        GCal-->>W: write config/session_schedule.json
        W->>G: Gate 1: emergency_mode.active flag
        W->>G: Gate 2: window + trigger check vs session_schedule.json
        alt outside windows or locked
            G-->>W: abort
        end
    end

    W->>G: Gate 4 (all): session.lock
    alt locked
        G-->>W: abort
    end

    W->>P: increment counter, write lock
    P->>P: nexus JWT refresh
    P->>P: behavioral_adapter.py → behavioral_context.txt
    P->>P: resolve_session_type.py → reads consecutive_philosophy.count\n→ selects philosophy/philosophy_creative/philosophy_blocker/philosophy_cap
    alt philosophy_cap (count≥3)
        P-->>W: abort — skip Claude launch
    end
    P->>P: loom session start → current_loom_session_id.txt

    P->>C: launch with augmented goal + persona
    C->>M: read latest_summary.md + learnings_digest.md
    C->>C: orient, choose execution/planning type
    C->>C: work tasks (check context + time between tasks)

    C->>M: write latest_summary.md (HOT STATE)
    C->>M: update progress.md, learnings.md, index.md
    C->>M: write sessions/YYYY-MM-DD_N.md
    C->>M: append session_log.csv
    C->>M: write analytics.db (analytics_write.py)
    C->>M: write state/reports/ (session_report.py)
    C->>M: loom session end --handoff

    C-->>W: exit
    W->>W: update consecutive_philosophy.count\n(increment if philosophy*, reset otherwise)
    W->>W: relationship_update.py (post-session)
    W->>W: remove session.lock
